g.title: j3187938208
g.text: Lo siento, Tláloc ran across the keys He has NO manners

g.title: j1860647007
g.text: Lol! I have a kavat at home that does that, only last time she sat on the orbiter controls she broke them. ... Kavats weigh a bit more than rats...

g.title: j4090841145
g.text: He is always in the middle of things
Or nibbling on things he shouldn't be

g.title: j2073457147
g.text: Named after the ancient god of rain

g.title: j95565786
g.text: If I wanted to be friends with your rats, how would I do that?

g.title: j2668717742
g.text: How hard is it to take care of rats?

g.title: j1593298804
g.text: I'm trying to picture one of your rats in battle and I'm laughing my ass off.

g.title: j1309457509
g.text: I do! Kavats, kubrows, predasites, vulpaphyla, all types of sub-species.

g.title: j1878276953
g.text: They're less pets and more "murder animals" I keep around to help me.

g.title: j800839592
g.text: The rat, not the god jajaja
I don't need that kind of bad mojo

g.title: j2874926933
g.text: Like all creatures, food is the easiest path to love jaja
But if you hold them, do not grab them, let them explore and get used to you
Make clicking noises not kissy noises, kissy noises sound like bad squeaks to them

g.title: j874196459
g.text: They need a big cage with bedding, places to hide, things to do, things to chew on
They are social and need exercise, so I take them out of their cage a lot to roam

g.title: j2084317842
g.text: Tláloc has the attitude but not the size for sure jaja
Maybe we could make them little battle armor
No, they are too small and fragile
It would break my heart if anything happened to them

g.title: j3200721611
g.text: Those names mean nothing to me, babas
But do you care about them?

g.title: j3678231931
g.text: Of course I do. They fight beside me, sure, but I love them.

g.title: j4044464269
g.text: In the same way I care about the guns I own.

g.title: j822595413
g.text: Just as bad as that Entrati cabrón
Abusing and then abandoning those poor Cavia

g.title: j3942129813
g.text: How many rats do you have?

g.title: j69223960
g.text: Not much to ask for when you get so much in return from them
Ni modo, some people do not understand I suppose

g.title: j3191125613
g.text: I should introduce you to some of my pets sometime.

g.title: j4078486499
g.text: Animals deserve nothing but love and loyalty
They fight for you because that is what they feel for you
I am sure my panquecitos would fight for me if they could jajaja

g.title: j1587291372
g.text: Just as bad as that Entrati cabrón
Taking the love of that man and using him for his own gain

g.title: j1737695311
g.text: Just as bad as that Entrati cabrón
Starting a family only to abandon them when they were of no use

g.title: j2486827931
g.text: And maybe you can show me some of your strange pets in return

g.title: j1231478937
g.text: And maybe then I will introduce you to my rats in return
